results.name: Self-inverse permutation of natural numbers induced by the automorphism DeepReverse_et_RotateHandshakes! acting on the parenthesizations encoded by A014486.
comment: This automorphism reflects non-crossing handshakes (the interpretation n of Stanley's exercise 19) over the diagonal that goes through corner at "1 o'clock".
link: A. Karttunen, Gatomorphisms (Includes the complete Scheme program for computing this sequence)
